message: Focus on creating initial combinations that yield 30 value. The most reliable way to achieve this is often by combining one natural ingredient with one artificial ingredient, regardless of soft/hard. Once an item has a value of 30, use the 'frame' tool on it to consistently reach 50. Do NOT use the 'frame' tool on an item that is already framed, as this will drastically reduce its value and ruin the frame. The 'scissors' tool is very risky; it can sometimes salvage a negatively valued item to 0 or 30, but often significantly reduces the value of already positive or 'cut' items. Avoid combining complex items that already have negative values.
